<number box="[1333,1375,511,536]" pageId="8" pageNumber="465" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5–6</number>
pairs of scutellar marginal setae, legs broadly reddish yellow, and abdomen broadly reddish yellow.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
